{"id":5861,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">最近读李普的新著《洋女婿土老帽》。打开目录，一股清新之气扑面而来，强大的吸引力使我急切地打开书本，一篇一篇地读下去。这本书是李普近年来对一些问题反思的收获。作者说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">思考给我快乐，这快乐我愿与读者共享。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">读这本书时，我的确分享了快乐。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　在上个世纪三十年代，李普就参加了中国共产党领导的抗日救亡运动，很快就成为中国共产党的一员。他在重庆《新华日报》（中国共产党在国民党政府陪都的机关报）上，开辟了《解放区漫谈》专栏，发表了大量介绍延安和其它抗日民主根据地的文章，使国统区的爱国青年向往不已。解放战争期间，他是刘邓大军的随军记者，随刘伯承转战南北，记录下了胜利的篇章。他以极大的喜悦迎接革命的胜利，并且报道了开国大典有盛况。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　然而，他并没有永远停留在革命胜利的喜悦之中，他的思想是与时俱进的。他在这本书中说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我一生经历了两次思想解放，或者叫两次思想革命。一次是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年代由爱好文艺而爱好普罗文艺，同时加上不愿当亡国奴而参加抗日民主救亡运动，这样就逐渐接受了马克思主义。第二次是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1978</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年关于实践是检验真理的唯一标准的讨论。．．．．我这第二次思想解放也是一个长过程。我好比进了一次大学，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1978</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的讨论好比是我的一年级，到今天我也不认为毕业了。我可以说至今天天在享受获得新知的快乐，天天在享受破旧立新的喜悦。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（《黎澍老夫子》）他还写道：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">二十年前真理标准的讨论使我恍然大悟，原来自己已经多年不用脑子，不想问题了。然后又悟到，那时想还是想了的，不过是在既定框框里想，是预先肯定它正确。那时的想，其实只是领会，只是学习，只是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">跟</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，跳出了这个框框，便豁然开朗，进入了一个新天地。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（《思考的快乐》）他在其它文章中也谈到第二次思想解放使他有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">豁然开朗的欣喜，如梦初醒的振奋</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　从这本书里可以看到，他的思想的确</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">进入了一个新天地</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。读他的书，简直是在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">新天地</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">里漫游。在这里，多年来在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">框框</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">里已成定论的东西，经过他的反思以后，升华到大彻大悟的新境界。而这些的新境界，饱含着</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">80</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">岁老人的深刻和智慧，使得新思想显得老到和凝重。在这片</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">新天地</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">里，处处可以看到对中国过去和未来的思索，对社会进步的追求。他高呼：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">五四新文化运动还远没有完成，我们还必须高举民主和科学的旗帜前进！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（《胡适的一番老话》）他呼唤</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">告别万岁</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，主张</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">依法治国</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。而依法治国</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">首先是法律至上，宪法至上。其次是宪法和法律保护人民的种种权利不受侵犯，是人权至上。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（《路漫漫兮</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">依法治国</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">》）自由，民主，法治，人权，科学，这些人类普适性的东西，我们曾一度抛弃过，说得轻一点是淡忘了，如今，在老人的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">新天地</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">里，成了最强的音符。这些，也是当今中国进步人士最强的呼声。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　在北京这个地方，进入老年后大彻大悟的不只是李普一人。这本书中有纪念他的老友黎澍、胡绳、夏衍、廖沫沙的情深意切的篇章，也有记述他和李锐、于光远、李慎之等老友交往的重要且有趣的文字。这些老人中除了李锐能够保留一些独立思考之外，其他人也是第二次思想解放以后觉醒的。黎澍觉醒得更早一些，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1984</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年就发表了题为《论历史的创造及其它》的长篇论文，否定了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人民群众是历史的创造者</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">这个长期奉为金科玉律的论断，在当时简直是放了一颗</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">精神原子弹</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。胡绳则觉醒得晚一些，正如他自己在晚年说的，在很长的一段时间内，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">为顺应潮流，我写过若干与实际不符合、在理论上站不住脚的文章。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（《胡绳全书》第二卷</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">引言</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">），李普一度</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">感到他在作文处事中那拘谨的一面大大发展了，这使我渐渐产生一种惋惜的心情</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，直到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">80</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年代，李普还直率地对他说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">你是个学者，还是回书斋做学问的好。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">但胡绳却有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">拉上了，推不掉</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的苦衷。然而，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1998</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年胡绳发表的《毛泽东新民主主义论再评价》的大文章，使李普</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">如坐春风</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">好像又看到了当年的胡绳</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。这里说的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">当年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">是指他们在《新华日报》共事的时候，那时他们都是民主斗士。李普写道：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">胡绳觉醒了，站起来了，我感到十分庆幸。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（《悼胡绳》）在李普这本新著中，活灵活现地描述了这一些老人的第二次觉醒。这些描述，应当是中国当代思想史上重要的、生动的史料。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　史学<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"家蔡仲德\">家蔡仲德</st1:PersonName>教授研究冯友兰，提出了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">冯友兰现象</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">一说，认为冯氏一生可分为三个阶段：早年实现自我，中间失去自我，晚年回归自我。李普认为胡绳也经历了这三个阶段。其实，李普本人和一大批老人，也经历了这三个阶段。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　我曾经在一篇文章中，称这些老人是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">两头真</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的人物：年青时代为追求真理真诚地参加革命，离休以后大彻大悟真诚地面对社会现实。李普的朋友中大多是这样的人。李普是新闻界的前辈，也是我的老领导。但他当官时我不认识他。这并不是他高高在上，而归于我的一种特殊的过敏症，对官员的面孔和眼神过敏，所以总是远离高官。其实，李普并没有使我</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">过敏</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的那种面孔和眼神。黎澍曾说李普</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在下级面前不自以为是上级，在上级面前不自以为是下级</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，我还得加上一句：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在年轻人面前不自以为是老人，在晚辈面前不自以为是长辈</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。我们第一次认识是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1985</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年在养马岛休假，我们两人在海边捡石头，他和我一样光着脚，捡到一块好石头那种欣喜的样子，就像孩子一样天真无邪。那时我向他谈了一些当时主流舆论视为叛逆的言论，没想到竟引起了他的共鸣。我们年龄相差</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">多岁，但我总是对他李普李普地称呼，因为我们谈话时，总是忘了年龄的差别。李普的老朋友相聚，他有时叫上我，由此我结识了一批</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">两头真</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的老人。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　这些</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">两头真</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的老人可爱得很。记得是去年春夏之交，李普夫妇、黄宗江夫妇、李锐、苏仲湘、常大林等到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">皇城老妈</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">吃川菜，李普呼我同往。席间，谈古论今，口无遮拦，滉筹交错，笑声阵阵。他们脱口而出的经历，常常就有史料价值。李锐谈到延安一段往事：有一次，毛泽东问师哲：皇帝和总统有什么不同？师哲用政治学的知识讲了个一二三，毛泽东哈哈大笑，说：其实是一样的！李锐讲完了这个故事，大家沉默了许久。还是戏剧家黄宗江用他的幽默打破了沉默，他讲到和李普在青岛上中学时办小报批评时政的一则趣闻，引起了一阵笑声，他又突然冒出了这样一句话：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我们这些人一辈子走了一条之字路。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，他站起来，挥动长长的手臂划了一个</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">之</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">字。我觉得这个</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">之</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">字，就是<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"蔡仲德\">蔡仲德</st1:PersonName>教授说的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">三个阶段</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的形象化。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　社会发展是曲折的。人们的思想要与时俱进，也不得不走</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">之</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">字路。如果一条直道儿走到底，那就会脱离社会进步的主线。不过，李普这本书告诉我，与时俱进不是跟潮流，而是对社会进步的追求，对真理的追求。与时俱进要付出代价，这代价有时还十分沉重。这本书中所谈到的人都是付出过代价的。譬如李锐，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1959</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年在庐山会议上受到错误批判，被定为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭德怀反党集团</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">成员，撤消一切职务，开除出党，下放劳动。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">期间关在秦城监狱</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年。他其所以这样，不是跟潮流，而是逆一时之潮流。但从大的历史时期来看，他是与时俱进的。要做到这一点很不容易，除了独立思考以外，还要有一点献身精神。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　<FONT face=楷体_GB2312>　（《洋女婿土老帽》，李普著，福建人民出版社</FONT></SPAN><FONT face=楷体_GB2312><SPAN lang=EN-US>2001</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月出版，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">瞻顾从书</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第三辑）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>","title":"在新天地里漫游――读《洋女婿土老帽》","time":1248023532000}